{"tid":840132,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山齊士應該很後悔當初沒有選擇加盟曼城。","createTime":"2018-09-28T12:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T02:58:00.000Z","uid":153341,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8985f2dd4a4723c9642f00c907aab1e89b4dd838","tid":840132,"uid":153341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"曼聯名宿保羅-恩斯表示，現在山齊士應該很後悔當初沒有選擇加盟曼城。<br />\n<br />\n「山齊士會後悔自己沒有去曼城，如果他去了那裡，那對他來說絕對是最佳的轉會。曼城踢得自由流暢，崇尚攻勢足球，在那裡你會被鼓勵帶球推進。而在曼聯，球會的足球層面，以及情緒方面都是負面的，有這樣的氣氛你不能責怪他。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「他加盟了一支問題多多的球隊。如果他想要因為沒去曼城，或者離開阿仙奴而後悔，我不會感到意外。他沒有在曼聯成功也不出奇。」"},{"pid":"781dce58bcddfe9bf9af9d0fc0488ca1d1fcec4a","tid":840132,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"佢想走阿記唔放咋噃"},{"pid":"ecddd7ce71b0acda5ea8634e17a31af672fdc1f0","tid":840132,"uid":10089,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"去曼城起碼痴返個英超先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88d875dde8b26ebbc49ebc5fca4c87f4250cc63","tid":840132,"uid":27416,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"山神睇唔起金錢足球無底蘊既球隊"},{"pid":"101bbfa3c79344d987e4a23e162225b8265d31f4","tid":840132,"uid":158791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"賺多左錢喎,點會後悔"},{"pid":"09f2eb9bd76101531b93b5c8b51c5e74bfcc25aa","tid":840132,"uid":161731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:49:57.000Z","msg":"根本係爺爺落order 叫佢去最聯"},{"pid":"f98efb547e310d1ac324e6683980b67eb532ce2b","tid":840132,"uid":4957,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:49:57.000Z","msg":"你估人地真係會買你咩 抬價玩鳩曼狗咋"},{"pid":"abcbb463cbdfe3f9aa8d367b952c5dfff2d2e069","tid":840132,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"山狗好似咩都贏過哂<br />\n緊係去孩比高人工"},{"pid":"451efe6d80be6ebb3473e40d98a2c2e75a45ae